[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35682]Elite rogue armour UNP[/url]


How to use :

1. Download and open the .rar file
2. Ive packed everything in nicely so all you have to do is either drag the data folder into your skyrim directory or open the data folder and drag that folder into your data folder.
3. Load up racemenu, then go to sculpt and load up Aaliyah the head mesh
4. Go to presets and load up Aaliyah the preset, all done! :)
